@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Broker Commission Tracking Process

actor "Môi giới" as Broker
boundary "Broker Commissions UI" as UI
control "Broker Controller" as BrokerCtrl
database "Broker Commissions Table" as Commissions
database "Broker Leads Table" as Leads
database "Rooms Table" as Rooms
database "Users Table" as Users

Broker -> UI: Mở trang hoa hồng
UI -> BrokerCtrl: GET /api/broker/commissions
BrokerCtrl -> Commissions: Lấy hoa hồng theo broker_id

alt Bảng hoa hồng chưa được khởi tạo
  Commissions --> BrokerCtrl: Table missing / schema cache error
  BrokerCtrl --> UI: []
  UI --> Broker: Hiển thị chưa có hoa hồng
else Truy vấn thất bại
  Commissions --> BrokerCtrl: Database error
  BrokerCtrl --> UI: 500 Server Error
  UI --> Broker: Không thể tải hoa hồng
else Truy vấn thành công
  Commissions -> Leads: Lấy thông tin lead liên quan
  Commissions -> Rooms: Lấy thông tin phòng liên quan
  Commissions -> Users: Lấy thông tin tenant liên quan
  Leads --> Commissions: Lead info
  Rooms --> Commissions: Room info
  Users --> Commissions: Tenant info
  Commissions --> BrokerCtrl: Danh sách hoa hồng
  BrokerCtrl --> UI: Commission list
  UI --> Broker: Hiển thị trạng thái hoa hồng
end

@enduml
